name: typescript
memorySetupCommand: gcloud run services update typescript-lamp-control-api --project "$GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT" --region europe-west1 --remove-env-vars DATABASE_URL
dbSetupCommand: gcloud run services update typescript-lamp-control-api --project "$GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT" --region europe-west1 --update-env-vars DATABASE_URL="$BENCHMARK_DATABASE_URL"
